    "title": "Markdown",
    "content": "# Markdown\n\nLearn how to use Markdown effectively in your documentation.\n\n## Overview\n\nMarkdown is a lightweight markup language for creating formatted text.\n\n## Key Features\n\n- Basic syntax\n- Extended features\n- MDX components\n- Code blocks",
